metadata.name: RAREPEPE
metadata.description:
Wrapped RAREPEPE Card 1, Series 1 - The Nakamoto Card - only 300 issued, September 2016.

This is a wrapped Counterparty asset. The Counterparty seed phrase is embedded in the vault.

You can trade this wrapped RAREPEPE on OpenSea and other Ethereum marketplaces, as long as you don't crack open the vault.

Once the vault is opened, you have the Counterparty wallet seed phrase to access your RAREPEPE on https://rarepepewallet.com, but you can no longer trade the wrapped asset on Ethereum.
